&lt;section class=&quot;js_blockquote_digest&quot;&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;“你没在中国生活过，也没在香港生活过。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;香港不是我们的后院，你现在谈论的是别人的后院。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;在中国，有6亿人口看NBA，比美国人口还多两亿，人家伸手喂你，你这是咬他们的手。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

